text: Jack Whitver (born September 4, 1980) is an American businessman and Republican politician. He has been a member of the Iowa Senate since 2011. From 2017 to 2018, he was President of the Iowa Senate. In 2018, he was elected State Senate Majority Leader. Whitver was born in Knoxville, Iowa. In May 2024, Whitver announced that he was diagnosed with a brain tumor. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Iowa Category:Businesspeople from Iowa Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
